# Pre-built binaries (ratchet.exe, ratchet-gui.exe) ARE committed on purpose so downloaders can run
# the host immediately via the launchers - do NOT ignore *.exe here.

# Runtime / dev cruft
ratchet-gui.error.log
*.pdb
_*

# Per-instance runtime, all regenerated - never commit these (they appear inside instances/examples):
#   .index/  the BM25 / embedding search cache (KbIndex)
#   runs/    per-chain-run state (runs/<id>/step-NNN.json)
.index/
runs/

# Per-session memory (written by the chat; not source).
NOTES.md

